Plate stress dummy grid

Source: R/draw_eulerpole.R
dummy.Rd

Creates a dummy grid for small circles, great circles, and loxodromes of an Euler pole

Usage

smallcircle_dummy(n)

greatcircle_dummy(n)

loxodrome_dummy(n, angle, sense)

Arguments

n

Number of curves

angle

Direction of loxodromes (in degree)

sense

Sense of loxodromes 'sinistral' or 'dextral' for 'clockwise' or 'counterclockwise' loxodromes, respectively

Value

data.frame

Examples

smallcircle_dummy(10)
